    "client_msg_id": "a1b2176a-5e03-44f5-8bdb-9f77de1bcfd6",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Reminds me of the discussion of the difference between education and propaganda in <https://consilienceproject.org/we-dont-make-propaganda-they-do/>. The goal of education is to bring the student to the level of the teacher. The goal of propaganda is to maintain an epistemic gap. Teaching programming within predefined limits is then closer to propaganda than to education.",
